SINGAPORE: India tenders to buy kerosene for October arrival.India tenders to buy kerosene for October arrival.State-owned Indian Oil Corp (IOC) has issued a tender to buy superior kerosene for delivery in October, traders said on Tuesday.The tender seeks 30,000-tonne cargoes for delivery to Bombay on the Indian west coast and 45,000-tonne cargoes for delivery to Madras or Haldia on the east coast.The cargoes are to be delivered in a 10-day range.The tender closes on September 5 and offers should be valid until September 6.IOC cancelled its two tenders for September and August deliveries.  --Singapore Newsroom (+65-8703084)